query:
SELECT DISTINCT c.id, c.nome
FROM clientes c
INNER JOIN produtos p ON c.id = p.clienteId
WHERE c.projectId = 1 AND c.pesquisaId = 1
ORDER BY c.id
LIMIT 50;
